#: data/moe.nyarchlinux.updater.desktop.in:2
#: data/moe.nyarchlinux.updater.metainfo.xml.in:6 src/window.ui:8
msgid "Nyarch Updater"
msgstr "Nyarch 更新程序"

#: data/moe.nyarchlinux.updater.desktop.in:3
msgid "Keep your Nyarch Linux system up to date"
msgstr "让你的 Nyarch Linux 保持最新喵！"

#: data/moe.nyarchlinux.updater.metainfo.xml.in:7
msgid "Utility tool for updating your Nyarch Linux system"
msgstr "可以更新 Nyarch Linux 的高级工具"

#: data/moe.nyarchlinux.updater.metainfo.xml.in:9
msgid ""
"A linux guided tool for updating your Arch packages, Flatpaks, AUR Packages "
"and Nyarch releases in a beautiful and easy GUI."
msgstr ""
"一款 Linux 向导式图形工具，可以很轻松地更新 Arch、Flatpak、AUR 包"
"以及 Nyarch 发行版喵~。"

#: data/moe.nyarchlinux.updater.gschema.xml:12
msgid "The AUR helper Updater will use. Must be one of the supported choices."
msgstr "Nyarch 更新程序将会使用某种 AUR 助手进行更新，但是这个 AUR 助手必须是受支持的选项之一。"

#: data/moe.nyarchlinux.updater.gschema.xml:13 src/settings.ui:20
msgid "AUR Helper"
msgstr "AUR 助手"

#: data/moe.nyarchlinux.updater.gschema.xml:24
msgid "The command used to run system updates."
msgstr "运行系统更新的命令。"

#: data/moe.nyarchlinux.updater.gschema.xml:25 src/settings.ui:37
msgid "System Update Command"
msgstr "系统更新命令"

#: src/faq.ui:8 src/faq.ui:32
msgid "FAQ & Common Issues"
msgstr "常见的问题"

#: src/faq.ui:45
msgid "What is this app?"
msgstr "这个程序是做什么的？"

#: src/faq.ui:56
msgid ""
"Nyarch Updater is a utility application designed to help you keep your "
"system up to date! It allows package updates, flatpak updates, and most "
"importantly, Nyarch release updates."
msgstr "Nyarch 更新程序是一款帮助您保持系统最新的实用工具！它支持软件包更新、Flatpak 更新，以及最最重要的 Nyarch 发行版更新喵！"

#: src/faq.ui:74
msgid ""
"Clicking buttons such as \"execute command\" or \"show commands\" does "
"nothing"
msgstr "点击“执行命令”或“显示命令”等按钮没有反应。"

#: src/faq.ui:85
msgid ""
"This is a known issue that we are trying to fix. In the meantime, restarting "
"the app should make it work. I would say: restart it until it works, and "
"until we fix it."
msgstr "这是一个正在尝试修复的已知问题，重新启动应该可以正常工作...大概喵。如果不可以的话那就不停地重启，一直到它正常运行为止！我们已经在尽快修复了喵...别急喵..."

#: src/faq.ui:103
msgid "Executing a command did nothing"
msgstr "执行此命令没有效果...怎么回事呢？"

#: src/faq.ui:114
msgid ""
"Something went wrong here. Click \"show command\" and execute it yourself. "
"If it persists, please report it in the Discord or the Github."
msgstr "不好，出错了喵！你需要点击“显示命令”并手动执行。如果问题依旧发生了，请在 Discord 或 GitHub 上反馈喵。"

#: src/faq.ui:132
msgid ""
"The application keeps asking me to update my release even though I did all "
"the steps"
msgstr "即使我完成了所有步骤，应用仍然要求我更新发行版。"

#: src/faq.ui:143
msgid ""
"Something went wrong here, again. Don't worry, it's probably not your fault! "
"Check if you didn't skip the \"update version file\" step! If you didn't and "
"it still does not work, copy the command shown with \"Show Command\", and "
"run it after finishing the steps on your preferred terminal emulator. Then "
"restart updater to see the changes!"
msgstr ""
"又出错啦！别担心，这很可能不是你的问题喵。\n"
"请先检查是否跳过了“更新版本文件”这一步喵。\n"
"如果没跳过但仍然无效，请点击“显示命令”，把命令复制下来喵。\n"
"然后在完成所有更新步骤之后，在你最喜欢的终端里手动运行它喵。\n"
"运行完毕后，重启更新程序，问题应该就解决了喵！"

